book.title: Underworld (Resident Evil #4)
book.description:
Storyline: 
 As our heroes get closer to the truth behind the conspiracy, they storm a vast underground lab in the desert, hoping to find a way to stop the experiments of the Umbrella Corporation -- and their latest living weapons -- once and for all.
book.author: S.D. Perry
